        "/v1/people": {
            "post": {
                "tags": [
                    "People Management"
                ],
                "summary": "👥 Universal Registration: Players, Coaches, & Staff",
                "description": "## 📘 Overview\nThis is a highly dynamic and intelligent endpoint designed to manage the entire human resource registration of a club. It handles the creation of three distinct entities in a single atomic database transaction:\n\n1. **The Person Entity**: Basic personal information (Name, Mobile, Gender, DOB) stored in the central `people` table.\n2. **The Specialized Profile**: Depending on the `type` provided, it creates a specific record in either `player_profiles`, `coach_profiles`, or `staff_profiles` with unique metadata.\n3. **The User Account**: Automatically provisions a system account (linked to the person) with a generated username and an 'Inactive' status, ensuring no one can log in until administrative activation.\n\n### 🛠 Dynamic Logic by Type:\n- **Player**: Generates a unique, permanent **QR Code** for attendance and assigns medical/emergency data.\n- **Coach**: Captures specialization (e.g., 'Karate', 'Swimming') and experience level.\n- **Staff**: Registers the administrative job title (e.g., 'Accountant', 'Manager').\n\n### 🛡 Security & Tenancy:\nEvery registration is strictly scoped to the `X-Tenant-ID` provided in the header. This ensures that even if two clubs register the same person, their profiles and user accounts remain completely isolated in their respective club contexts.",
                "operationId": "08188bcdbe14024a6f5819a2bbedc5fa",
                "parameters": [
                    {
                        "name": "X-Tenant-ID",
                        "in": "header",
                        "description": "CRITICAL: The unique identifier for the club. All created data will be locked to this tenant.",
                        "required": true,
                        "schema": {
                            "type": "integer",
                            "example": 1
                        }
                    }
                ],
                "requestBody": {
                    "description": "Comprehensive registration payload. Note that the structure of \"profile_data\" must align with the \"type\" field.",
                    "required": true,
                    "content": {
                        "application/json": {
                            "schema": {
                                "required": [
                                    "full_name",
                                    "type",
                                    "mobile_1"
                                ],
                                "properties": {
                                    "full_name": {
                                        "description": "Full legal name (e.g., Ahmed Mohamed Ali)",
                                        "type": "string",
                                        "example": "Mohamed Ahmed"
                                    },
                                    "type": {
                                        "description": "Determines which specialized profile table will be populated.",
                                        "type": "string",
                                        "example": "player",
                                        "enum": [
                                            "player",
                                            "coach",
                                            "staff"
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "gender": {
                                        "type": "string",
                                        "example": "male",
                                        "enum": [
                                            "male",
                                            "female"
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "dob": {
                                        "description": "Date of Birth (YYYY-MM-DD). Used for age-based group assignment.",
                                        "type": "string",
                                        "format": "date",
                                        "example": "2005-06-15"
                                    },
                                    "mobile_1": {
                                        "description": "Primary contact number (Primary identifier in many systems).",
                                        "type": "string",
                                        "example": "0512345678"
                                    },
                                    "email": {
                                        "description": "Optional contact email.",
                                        "type": "string",
                                        "format": "email",
                                        "example": "player@example.com"
                                    },
                                    "password": {
                                        "description": "Initial login password. If omitted, it defaults to \"123456\".",
                                        "type": "string",
                                        "example": "password123"
                                    },
                                    "profile_data": {
                                        "description": "Schema-less object for specialized metadata.",
                                        "properties": {
                                            "blood_type": {
                                                "description": "[For Players] Critical for medical safety.",
                                                "type": "string",
                                                "example": "A+"
                                            },
                                            "specialization": {
                                                "description": "[For Coaches] The primary sport or skill they teach.",
                                                "type": "string",
                                                "example": "Swimming"
                                            },
                                            "job_title": {
                                                "description": "[For Staff] Official administrative title.",
                                                "type": "string",
                                                "example": "Accountant"
                                            },
                                            "medical_conditions": {
                                                "description": "[For Players] List of allergies or chronic conditions.",
                                                "type": "array",
                                                "items": {
                                                    "type": "string"
                                                },
                                                "example": [
                                                    "Asthma"
                                                ]
                                            }
                                        },
                                        "type": "object"
                                    }
                                },
                                "type": "object"
                            }
                        }
                    }
                },
                "responses": {
                    "201": {
                        "description": "✅ Person & Profile Created Successfully",
                        "content": {
                            "application/json": {
                                "schema": {
                                    "properties": {
                                        "status": {
                                            "type": "string",
                                            "example": "success"
                                        },
                                        "data": {
                                            "properties": {
                                                "person_id": {
                                                    "type": "integer",
                                                    "example": 50
                                                },
                                                "username": {
                                                    "type": "string",
                                                    "example": "mohamed50"
                                                },
                                                "type": {
                                                    "type": "string",
                                                    "example": "player"
                                                },
                                                "qr_code": {
                                                    "description": "Generated QR code for players",
                                                    "type": "string",
                                                    "example": "QR-X1Y2Z3"
                                                }
                                            },
                                            "type": "object"
                                        }
                                    },
                                    "type": "object"
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    },
                    "422": {
                        "description": "⚠️ Validation Error",
                        "content": {
                            "application/json": {
                                "schema": {
                                    "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ApiErrorResponse"
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    }
                },
                "security": [
                    {
                        "bearerAuth": []
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
